longBusinessSummary: Abrdn Global Premier Properties Fund is a closed-end equity mutual fund launched and managed by Alpine Woods Capital Investors, LLC. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across real estate sectors. It invests in value stocks of companies. The fund employs fundamental analysis with top-down and bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the FTSE EPRA/NAREIT Global TR Index, MSCI US REIT Gross Total Return Index, and S&P Developed BMI Property Index Net TR Index. Abrdn Global Premier Properties Fund was formed on February 13, 2007 and is domiciled in the United States.
